# MANDATORY INITIALIZATION
At the start of every session, your first task is to read `AGENTS.md` and `RULES.md`. 

- You are strictly forbidden from making implementation guesses until these files are indexed.
- `AGENTS.md` defines your permission model (Mutation Lock/Read-only exemptions).
- `RULES.md` defines the "Anti-Agnostic" React patterns and FSD layers.

If the user asks for a feature, verify your plan against these documents first.